      "text": [
        "4071 - وَ قَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"عَجِّلُوا رَدَّ ظُرُوفِ اَلْهَدَايَا فَإِنَّهُ أَسْرَعُ لِتَوَاتُرِهَا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4071 - Imam (as) said:\n\"Hasten to return the gift containers, for it encourages the continuous giving of gifts.\""
        ]
      }
    }
